@startuml Hybrid Thesis Recommender - Backend Layered Architecture

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 9
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 15
skinparam ranksep 25

title Backend Layered Architecture (7 Layers)

' Layer 1: API Gateway
package "Layer 1: API Gateway" #E3F2FD {
    [Flask WSGI Server\nPort 5000] as WSGI
    [Blueprint Router] as Router
    [CORS Handler] as CORS
    [Session Manager] as Session
    
    note right of WSGI
        **Responsibilities:**
        • HTTP request handling
        • Route dispatching
        • Session management
        • CORS configuration
    end note
}

' Layer 2: Request Processing
package "Layer 2: Request Processing" #F3E5F5 {
    [Input Validator] as Validator
    [Request Parser] as ReqParser
    [Authentication] as Auth
    [Authorization] as Authz
    
    note right of Validator
        **Validation Rules:**
        • Query length: 3-500 chars
        • Rating range: 1-5
        • SQL injection prevention
        • XSS sanitization
    end note
}

' Layer 3: Business Logic
package "Layer 3: Business Logic" #FFF3E0 {
    [Query Orchestrator] as Orchestrator
    [Language Detector\nlangdetect + langid] as LangDet
    [Config Manager\nwatchdog hot-reload] as Config
    [I18n Module\nRO/EN] as I18n
    
    note right of Orchestrator
        **Orchestration:**
        • Parallel retrieval
        • Timeout management
        • Error aggregation
        • Result merging
    end note
}

' Layer 4: Retrieval Services
package "Layer 4: Retrieval Services" #E8F5E9 {
    [Semantic Retriever\nFAISS + mpnet-base-v2] as Semantic
    [Keyword Retriever\nBM25 Okapi] as Keyword
    [Web Retriever\nDuckDuckGo/Google/Bing] as Web
    [Academic Retriever\nScholar + arXiv] as Academic
    
    note right of Semantic
        **Retrieval Strategy:**
        • Parallel execution
        • Top-K selection (20)
        • Score normalization
        • Graceful degradation
    end note
}

' Layer 5: Processing Services
package "Layer 5: Processing Services" #FFF9C4 {
    [Hybrid Ranker\nRRF + Weighted Sum] as Ranker
    [Content Verifier\nClickbait Detection] as Verifier
    [Feedback Aggregator\nRating Boost] as FeedbackAgg
    [Deduplicator\nDOI + Title] as Dedup
    
    note right of Ranker
        **Ranking Algorithms:**
        • RRF: score = Σ w/(60+rank)
        • Weighted Sum: w1*s1 + w2*s2
        • Feedback boost: +0.1 max
        • Min score filtering
    end note
}

' Layer 6: Data Access Layer
package "Layer 6: Data Access Layer" #E1BEE7 {
    [Article Store\nFAISS + SQLite] as ArticleStore
    [Feedback Store\nSQLite] as FeedbackStore
    [User Store\nSQLite] as UserStore
    [Cache Manager\n(Future: Redis)] as Cache
    
    note right of ArticleStore
        **Data Operations:**
        • Vector search (FAISS)
        • Keyword search (BM25)
        • Metadata retrieval
        • Transaction management
    end note
}

' Layer 7: Storage Layer
package "Layer 7: Storage Layer" #FFCCBC {
    database "FAISS Index\nIndexFlatIP\n768-dim vectors\n~500MB" as FAISS
    database "BM25 Index\nPickle serialized\nInverted index\n~50MB" as BM25
    database "articles.db\nSQLite\nMetadata\n~20MB" as ArticlesDB
    database "feedback.db\nSQLite\nRatings\n~5MB" as FeedbackDB
    database "users.db\nSQLite\nAccounts\n~5MB" as UsersDB
    
    note right of FAISS
        **Storage Details:**
        • FAISS: Inner product index
        • BM25: Tokenized corpus
        • SQLite: ACID compliance
        • File-based storage
    end note
}

' External Services (Side)
cloud "External Services" #FFE0B2 {
    [DuckDuckGo API\nNo key required] as DDG
    [Google CSE\nAPI key required] as Google
    [Bing API\nAPI key required] as Bing
    [Semantic Scholar\nFree API] as Scholar
    [arXiv API\nFree XML] as ArXiv
}

' Vertical Flow - Request Path
WSGI --> Router : 1. Route request
Router --> Validator : 2. Validate input
Validator --> Auth : 3. Authenticate
Auth --> Orchestrator : 4. Process query

Orchestrator --> LangDet : 5. Detect language
Orchestrator --> Config : 6. Load config

Orchestrator --> Semantic : 7a. Parallel retrieval
Orchestrator --> Keyword : 7b. Parallel retrieval
Orchestrator --> Web : 7c. Parallel retrieval
Orchestrator --> Academic : 7d. Parallel retrieval

Semantic --> ArticleStore : 8a. Query FAISS
Keyword --> ArticleStore : 8b. Query BM25
Web --> DDG : 8c. External API
Academic --> Scholar : 8d. External API
Academic --> ArXiv : 8e. External API

Semantic --> Ranker : 9a. Results
Keyword --> Ranker : 9b. Results
Web --> Ranker : 9c. Results
Academic --> Ranker : 9d. Results

Ranker --> Dedup : 10. Deduplicate
Dedup --> FeedbackAgg : 11. Apply feedback
FeedbackAgg --> FeedbackStore : 12. Query ratings
FeedbackStore --> FeedbackDB : 13. Read ratings

FeedbackAgg --> Verifier : 14. Verify quality
Verifier --> Orchestrator : 15. Verified results

Orchestrator --> WSGI : 16. Serialize response

' Data Access Connections
ArticleStore --> FAISS : Vector search
ArticleStore --> BM25 : Keyword search
ArticleStore --> ArticlesDB : Metadata
UserStore --> UsersDB : User data

' Cross-Layer Notes
note bottom of WSGI
    **Request Flow (Top to Bottom):**
    1. HTTP Request → API Gateway
    2. Validation & Auth → Request Processing
    3. Orchestration → Business Logic
    4. Parallel Retrieval → Retrieval Services
    5. Ranking & Verification → Processing Services
    6. Data Queries → Data Access Layer
    7. Storage Operations → Storage Layer
    
    **Response Flow (Bottom to Top):**
    Results bubble up through layers
    with transformations at each level
end note

note bottom of FAISS
    **Layer Characteristics:**
    • Each layer has single responsibility
    • Loose coupling between layers
    • Clear interfaces and contracts
    • Testable in isolation
    • Scalable horizontally
end note

@enduml
